安装社区版yum 源

yum install epel-release

安装cockpit

yum install cockpit

启动服务：

systemctl start cockpit

开机自启动：

systemctl enable cockpit.socket

设置防火墙：

firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit

firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit --permanent

firewall-cmd --reload

浏览器登录：

https://SERVER_IP:9090 

https://192.168.19.160:9090 
